  "description": "Saw src1 and Sine src2 at equal mix (srcMix=0.5) with competition ecology active (competitionStrength=0.7). When both voices are active, resources compete — one will begin to suppress the other based on amplitude and harmonic content. The Saw, being richer in harmonics, tends to dominate. Low-note attacks hear the competition as a subtle dynamic push-pull between sources.",
